          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "onTermination",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " callback is set, using task cancellation to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "terminate iteration of an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "AsyncStream",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " results in a call to this",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "callback.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Canceling an active iteration invokes the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "onTermination",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " callback",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "first, then resumes by yielding ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "nil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ". This means that you can perform",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "needed cleanup in the cancellation handler. After reaching a terminal",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "state as a result of cancellation, the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "AsyncStream",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " sets the callback",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "nil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
